                (:P3203_PAID_FLG = 'N' or :P3203_PAID_FLG is null)
                and (:P3203_GREENBUTTON_FLG = 'N' or :P3203_GREENBUTTON_FLG is null)
                ```
        }
        error {
            errorMessage: "If a workshop is a LiveLabs Sprint, it cannot have any other buttons. Either disable the other workshop types or disable LiveLabs Sprints. Contact Kevin Lazarz if you believe this is not the case for your workshop. "
        }
        serverSideCondition {
            type: expression
            plsqlExpression: :P3203_SPRINT_FLG = 'Y'
        }
    )

